scenes.description: The performers conclude the previous song and thank the audience.
Transition scene with stage lights and cheering.
MC section where Amane Kanata prepares for the next performance while other members chat.
Performance of the song 'GO! GO! MANIAC'.
Post-performance transition with instrumental background music.
